In 1858 , Django , a slave , is chained to a bunch of other slaves and being marched to Django's new owner 's estate in Texas by the Speck brothers . At nightfall , a German man in a dentist cart pulls up and hails the Speck brothers . man introduces himself as Dr. King Schultz . Schultz is clearly more intelligent and enlightened than the Specks . Schultz says Schultz is looking for a slave who can identify a band of wanted fugitives known as the Brittle brothers . Django announces that Django knows the Brittle brothers and can identify brothers . Schultz offers to buy Django , but Schultz's polite and educated manner rubs the ill-mannered Specks the wrong way , and Ace Speck threatens to shoot Schultz with Schultz's shotgun . In response , Schultz lowers Schultz's lantern , whips out a revolver , and shoots Ace , then Dicky 's horse , causing Dicky to fall off Dicky's horse . The horse carcass then lands on and crushes Dicky 's leg , leaving Dicky screaming in pain . Crippled , Dicky agrees to sell Django , and Schultz pays the man , gets an official title to Django , and prepares to ride off .